{"tid":1169853,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：我永遠是阿仙奴球迷","createTime":"2019-05-24T15:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T07:58:38.000Z","uid":142576,"like":102,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"9ffc4abe6772256bb7a0cfaab16ae2edc77173f5","tid":1169853,"uid":142576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"雲加表示永遠支持阿仙奴 米希達恩事件不應發生<br />\n<br />\n歐霸杯決賽將在下星期舉行，雲加近日接受采訪時談到了他對這場決賽的看法。<br />\n<br />\n雲加首先是談到了米希達恩的看法，他說道：&ldquo;這種事是不應該發生在足球世界裏的，實際上如果足球摻雜了政治他就不能好好的踢球了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n然後雲加又談到了最近飽受爭議的決賽場地巴庫，雲加表示：&ldquo;其實這件事對球隊來說沒什麽大問題，因為球隊的條件很好，他們有私人飛機，很好的商務座位。但是球迷們並不一樣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;我永遠支持阿仙奴。這是我的球隊。我把我的生命都獻給了它</span>，只不過我目前在專注於其他事情。我現在是一位阿仙奴球迷，我不會去評判什麽。他們贏了球我就開心，輸了我也會傷心，但是我同時也會和球會保持一定的距離。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我會重返足球世界的，一定會的。我將會擔任什麽職位、是否還會當主教練？現在我還不太清楚。但是我對足球的渴望還在。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;起初我說過我想馬上重新開始。在那之後，我想也許我應該先遠離足球一段時間。我得出的結論是，我想分享我在生活中學到的東西。在生命某個階段，去分享你所知道的，生命才有意義。所以生活到底是怎樣的&mdash;&mdash;是一直追求贏下比賽還是其他什麽的？這是我需要做出決定的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我會很快作出決定，我對足球依然有激情，足球是我認為自己唯一還比較了解的事情。我之前從事了40年的足球行業，很難說離開了就不會想念它。這很正常，但是當我想念足球的時候，我就會把精力放在生活中的其他事情上面。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爺爺的瑰寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fa0f07aa38beea35d2228ca13170be6593b071","tid":1169853,"uid":243093,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"雲加，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfd71ebf7171a253d72a303de234c59f30fbe30","tid":1169853,"uid":144571,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5507cf2a4bc8db3212635ffc2c3144d5453f18b1","tid":1169853,"uid":16015,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"Emery out<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752539f7baf4b83498a53e71677b6f097b15736f","tid":1169853,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"這是我的球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這是高安基的球隊先岩囉"},{"pid":"fe07010a28c2df7b208b34f61357565cdffefb92","tid":1169853,"uid":235174,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I read a lot, do a lot of different sports, daily, so that occupies me. <span style=\"color: red;\">I run 8-10 km a day.</span> I travelled a lot. I did a lot of game observation, charity, many conferences on football, on management, on motivation, on the meaning of life. I personally don&rsquo;t know what it means &hellip; I am always under stress a little bit but what was good is I don&rsquo;t have to get up or if I have an interesting lunch I don&rsquo;t have to leave because I have a commitment. I discovered that freedom of time in front of you. It is a good feeling.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2747d703358ec50f012ab23fb5fdc85630d97c07","tid":1169853,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T18:53:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f98b40d12bcb160de2f60abd0097fe3a18cc3c40","tid":1169853,"uid":9256,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"fe07010a28c2df7b208b34f61357565cdffefb92","tid":1169853,"uid":235174,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I read a lot, do a lot of different sports, daily, so that occupies me. <span style=\"color: red;\">I run 8-10 km a day.</span> I travelled a lot. I did a lot of game observation, charity, many conferences on football, on management, on motivation, on the meaning of life. I personally don&rsquo;t know what it means &hellip; I am always under stress a little bit but what was good is I don&rsquo;t have to get up or if I have an interesting lunch I don&rsquo;t have to leave because I have a commitment. I discovered that freedom of time in front of you. It is a good feeling.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:21:59.000Z","msg":"雲加：今晚天氣好好，有微風。但好累。"},{"pid":"bba24be2ab52509e2d7c63467faf7397f0a14cdc","tid":1169853,"uid":6327,"like":4,"dislike":46,"score":-42,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:30:51.000Z","msg":"死老野做保安都冇人請啊"},{"pid":"895eac5bf8021d1016fbd33c6486a521fa43ea09","tid":1169853,"uid":18624,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"bba24be2ab52509e2d7c63467faf7397f0a14cdc","tid":1169853,"uid":6327,"like":4,"dislike":46,"score":-42,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:30:51.000Z","msg":"死老野做保安都冇人請啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:34:43.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},{"pid":"4f85a03ea221bf57a9c940ff700d54c6faae2eac","tid":1169853,"uid":78074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T21:44:11.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真正第一風扇"},{"pid":"9dee9632b99d1aad1992393cb3161cd73512e9eb","tid":1169853,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T21:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2955103fd39025c020d1aca8f9df057d704a7c67","tid":1169853,"uid":14449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:26:04.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a103caf1075d2184cc577bd0679312dfe4a407","tid":1169853,"uid":203961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f98b40d12bcb160de2f60abd0097fe3a18cc3c40","tid":1169853,"uid":9256,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"fe07010a28c2df7b208b34f61357565cdffefb92","tid":1169853,"uid":235174,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I read a lot, do a lot of different sports, daily, so that occupies me. <span style=\"color: red;\">I run 8-10 km a day.</span> I travelled a lot. I did a lot of game observation, charity, many conferences on football, on management, on motivation, on the meaning of life. I personally don&rsquo;t know what it means &hellip; I am always under stress a little bit but what was good is I don&rsquo;t have to get up or if I have an interesting lunch I don&rsquo;t have to leave because I have a commitment. I discovered that freedom of time in front of you. It is a good feeling.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:21:59.000Z","msg":"雲加：今晚天氣好好，有微風。但好累。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3d32bdb9c13feae0558dfab3750b45b6e70e0f","tid":1169853,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba24be2ab52509e2d7c63467faf7397f0a14cdc","tid":1169853,"uid":6327,"like":4,"dislike":46,"score":-42,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:30:51.000Z","msg":"死老野做保安都冇人請啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11693b2171d6a0ff97c32ea6ad38a3fccf6f514f","tid":1169853,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:43:05.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.